            <thetext>The following Playground code should create a gradient from green to magenta:

var affe = new qx.ui.decoration.Decorator().set({
  startColor: &quot;rgb(0,255,0)&quot;,
  endColor: &quot;magenta&quot;
});

var w = new qx.ui.core.Widget().set({
  width: 100,
  height: 100,
  decorator: affe
});

this.getRoot().add(w, {top: 20, left: 20});

In IE 8, the colors are misinterpreted as blue and black instead.</thetext>
